# No Cursor git attribution

Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Co-authored-by: cursoragent`, `Made-with: Cursor`, or any Cursor/cursoragent trailer to commit messages, PRs, or code comments.

When committing, do not pass `--trailer` flags that attribute work to Cursor.
